Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.58,0:00:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實現了完全假想空間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.95,0:00:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.27,0:00:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本週的MMO Stream
